---Contact!---

Start Point: Speak to Sophanem outside of Redbelly Mine

Official Difficulty: Experienced

Description: A previously hidden door in Redbelly mine leads to a sprawling dungeon and temple to Peryite. Rid the temple of its inhabitants.

Official length: Short

Requirements: Completion of "Mine or Yours"

Items required: Combat Equipment

Enemies to defeat: Giant Chaurus (scales)

Quest Stages: 

Rewards: Keris Dagger, 2 levels in One-Handed, Two-Handed, Destruction, or Archery (can be chosen, can stack or choose separate)
